data.description: SEMI-FURNISHED TOWNHOME in highly sought after TRIO FIELDS in NAZARETH. 3 BEDROOMS/4 BATHS. UPGRADED FLOOR PLAN (Everglade model) w/MULTIPLE EXTRAS. LARGE extended LIVING ROOM. Ultra MODERN kitchen w/NEW STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES and ISLAND seating. EXPANSIVE AND BRIGHT second floor with PLENTY OF CLOSET SPACE. LOFT AREA for separate entertaining/work space. MASTER SUITE W/FULL BATH w/LARGE SOAKING TUB and DOUBLE SINKS. FINISHED DAYLIGHT BASEMENT w/HALF BATH. CENTRAL AC. 2 CAR GARAGE and REAR COMPOSITE DECK, all on a CORNER LOT. Make yourself at HOME in this PICTURESQUE neighborhood w/ LOW HOA fees and PLENTY OF BRIGHT, AIRY SPACE.
